; Date       Who  Description
; ----       ---  -----------
; 25-Aug-99  SBF  Created: all known keyboard IDs, KeyV reason codes, KeyV flags and low-level key numbers included
;

; Keyboard IDs.
KeyboardID_A500                 * 0
KeyboardID_Archimedes           * 1
KeyboardID_PC                   * 2
KeyboardID_RCMM                 * 3

; KeyV reason codes.
KeyV_KeyboardPresent            * 0
KeyV_KeyUp                      * 1
KeyV_KeyDown                    * 2
KeyV_NotifyLEDState             * 3
KeyV_EnableDrivers              * 4

; Flags in R1 of KeyV_NotifyLEDState
KeyV_LED_ScrollLock             * 1
KeyV_LED_NumLock                * 2
KeyV_LED_CapsLock               * 4

